id.comment: Select stmt that is parent of assign with pattern

query.querystr: stmt s; assign a; Select s such that Parent (s, a) pattern a ("x", _)

id.comment: Select assign with pattern that has while as parent

query.querystr: while w; assign a; Select a such that Parent (w, a) pattern a (_, _"x"_)

id.comment: Select assign with pattern that has if as parent

query.querystr: assign a; if ifs; Select a such that Parent (ifs, a) pattern a ("z", _)
